{"tid":2452714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國高官：中方代表譁眾取寵，公開作秀，違反禮節。","createTime":"2021-03-19T04:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T04:45:08.000Z","uid":227801,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a011dc30c0e4a9903419e8209b985c51fe8f7425","tid":2452714,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:11:58.000Z","msg":"[url]https://n<del><a href=\"http://ews.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581451-20210319.htm?spTabChangea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581451-20210319.htm%3FspTabChangea&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSje9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=d68a1585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ews.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581451-20210319.htm?spTabChangea</a></del>ble=0[/url]<br />\n中美開場發言激烈交鋒　雙方互相指責違反禮節<br />\n<br />\n中美高層官員在阿拉斯加會談開場發言時激烈交鋒，中方代表團官員事後指責美方，在先致開場白時嚴重超時，並對中國內外政策無理攻擊指責，挑起爭端，認為這樣不是待客之道，也不符合外交禮儀，中方對此作出嚴正回應。這名官員又說，中方帶著誠意，應邀到安克雷奇同美方進行戰略對話，並做好按雙方事先商定的程序和安排開展對話的準備。而美國一名高層官員就說，中方代表似乎有意譁眾取寵，公開作秀，違反禮節。這名官員說，雙方在會談前同意，開場發言只有兩分鐘，但最後變成超過一小時。<br />\n<br />\n2021-03-19 11:56:59"},{"pid":"9c4898dd9f0692f464fd18a9242b35b802c0ab6f","tid":2452714,"uid":282930,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:13:10.000Z","msg":"期望班生蕃有禮節？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8cc8713e6a665526ff33bb97681a219b608c3e3","tid":2452714,"uid":3967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/174051_5a680edb5fba807513deccf67f96a4f3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F174051_5a680edb5fba807513deccf67f96a4f3.gif&h=02093710&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb77b654298f9de8122a388fd967d1eeaca114ac","tid":2452714,"uid":61032,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:16:39.000Z","msg":"雙方在會談前同意，開場發言只有兩分鐘，但最後變成超過一小時。<br />\n<b